---
// Ported from Hero.tsx (Lottie via dotlottie web component)
---
<section class="pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-12 md:pb-16 px-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-light/30 via-background to-background">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 text-center lg:text-left">
        <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start opacity-0 slide-up-fade" style="--delay:0s">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider bg-accent-sage/15 text-accent-sage-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Starting at $1/day</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight md:leading-[1.15] text-foreground opacity-0 slide-up-fade" style="--delay:0.1s">
          Helping BC folks like you find the <span class="text-foreground">best coverage</span> for your situation
        </h1>

        <p class="text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 opacity-0 slide-up-fade" style="--delay:0.2s">
          Between work, the kids, and bills, life insurance often takes a back seat. Until you realize how quick and easy it is to get affordable coverage that protects your family and future.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-3 pt-2 opacity-0 slide-up-fade" style="--delay:0.3s">
          <button type="button" data-open-quiz data-magnetic class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-300 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-primary-foreground rounded-full px-5 md:px-6 h-10 md:h-11 w-full md:w-auto">
            Get My Coverage Recommendation
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-muted-foreground">Most Canadians overestimate life insurance by 3x. See what's right for you today.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mt-4 lg:mt-0 min-h-[300px] lg:min-h-[400px] opacity-0 slide-up-fade flex items-center justify-center" style="--delay:0.4s">
        <dotlottie-wc src="/assets/online-work.lottie" autoplay loop class="w-full h-full" style="transform:scale(1.25)"></dotlottie-wc>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
